:::Torca/Ratchet/Sideswipe/Orion:::

::Torca looks at Klant::
Torca: What were you getting at during the fight?
~~~~~
::My other Maximals have realized for the first time that the CF was gone::
Sideswipe: Well, there goes our home.
Ratchet: Yep. Just like the Ark.
Sideswipe: Remember back when we, along with Striker and Spears, were the 
only defenders of the Ark?
Ratchet: Yeah. Those were the days.... hmm. Striker and Spears. I miss those 
two as well.
Orion: Alright, quit the trip down memory lane! I think i can actually see 
things getting wavy!
Sideswipe: hey, Bluestreak was a big player in the old days. Least until he 
met Andromeda.
Orion: Ive already heard the stories from my parents a zillion times.  Thats 
all they ever talk about!
Ratchet: Well, i guess it's time to move on. Maybe when things quiet down, 
you can finally meet your uncle Prowl.
::Ratchet opens a comm to Iron Raptor::
Ratchet: Is there anyhting we can do commander?

--part1_b6.15ccc6b8.2838ab8c_boundary
